  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>Released on: 9/13/16 1:00 CT</p><p>This is a minor release with\u00a0a few bug fixes.</p><h3 id=\"id-1.8.5-InvoiceRemittance\">Invoice Remittance</h3><p>Tickets linked to an invoice that are removed from the invoice will no longer be updated with future invoice updates. In addition, the remittance\u00a0invoice item filters will filter the items appropriately once again.</p><h3 id=\"id-1.8.5-LocationLeaderboardPermissions\">Location Leaderboard Permissions</h3><p>The location leaderboard will now only show the locations\u00a0where a user is the manager (or admin).</p><h3 id=\"id-1.8.5-AccountantRolePermissions\">Accountant Role Permissions</h3><p>Give the accountant role permission to view customer data by default.</p><h3 id=\"id-1.8.5-TicketHistory,loadondemand\">Ticket History, load on demand</h3><p>To improve page load times, we no longer load the history\u00a0with every ticket view or\u00a0edit screen. Instead, a &quot;load history&quot; button is present where you may load the ticket history\u00a0only when you need it.</p>",
